{"tid":669342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冷氣裝完，開兩日就壞，維修錢應該邊個比？","createTime":"2018-05-18T11:17:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T18:12:43.000Z","uid":68346,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec116ce8816de51be04a2ac87e745ef25c808e6","tid":669342,"uid":68346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:17:19.000Z","msg":"事件大約係咁<br />\n<br />\n屋企裝修，搭棚換冷氣<br />\n裝完師父試過機，冇問題拆棚<br />\n到我收樓，開過機，冇事咁就攪掂收貨啦<br />\n<br />\n點知開機第二晚，部野就打柴出熱風，攪完一大輪，代理肯換機，但唔肯比棚錢，要我自付<br />\n<br />\n呢個情況，代理話只包部機<br />\n裝修話，我裝ja wo, 部機有問題唔關佢事<br />\n<br />\n咁我係咪唯有硬食幾千銀？有冇得經小額錢積，家居保呢啲去追番個棚錢呢？去消委會投訴又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n好似夾硬比人屈幾千蚊咁"},{"pid":"6a15cd328671d420b231c9b1782cf709cab7d0f1","tid":669342,"uid":184247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:18:47.000Z","msg":"你檢收左，棚費就走唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2c29a65adb0701ca2d3d3693b75680b12bbd9e","tid":669342,"uid":186420,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"代理同師傅都冇錯，係你硬食嫁啦，當你唔好彩"},{"pid":"af59b144109930e362d6eb800b236d52d543d7f4","tid":669342,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"屋企裝冷氣未試過要搭棚咁大場面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45b6f15f02dafff7eb414fdbe5a1996ec5b422fb","tid":669342,"uid":68346,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"開一晚幾千蚊。。。有冇咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9edebb977de885577a56c250ac249a62345746f3","tid":669342,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T11:39:15.000Z","msg":"裝咩機要搭棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a676233a92bdca8cfd06d0a733884a59e0e3dd8b","tid":669342,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af59b144109930e362d6eb800b236d52d543d7f4","tid":669342,"uid":16061,